    │       │   ├── function_kw (kind: TerminalFunction)
    │       │   │   ├── leading_trivia (kind: Trivia)
    │       │   │   │   ├── child #0 (kind: TokenSingleLineComment): '// Regular comment'
    │       │   │   │   ├── child #1 (kind: TokenNewline).
